                            content to {SITE_TITLE}, you grant us a
                            non-exclusive, worldwide, royalty-free license to
                            use, display, and distribute your content on our
                            platform.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- User-Generated Content -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:edit"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        User-Generated Content
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            Users may submit prompts and other content to the
                            website. By submitting content, you represent and
                            warrant that:
                        </p>
                        <ul class="space-y-2 pl-4">
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <iconify-icon
                                    icon="lucide:check"
                                    width="16"
                                    class="text-emerald-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                                ></iconify-icon>
                                <span
                                    >You own or have the necessary rights to the
                                    content</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <iconify-icon
                                    icon="lucide:check"
                                    width="16"
                                    class="text-emerald-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                                ></iconify-icon>
                                <span
                                    >The content does not infringe on any third
                                    party's rights</span
                                >
                            </li>
                            <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <iconify-icon
                                    icon="lucide:check"
                                    width="16"
                                    class="text-emerald-400 mt-1 flex-shrink-0"
                                ></iconify-icon>
                                <span
                                    >The content is not harmful, offensive, or
                                    illegal</span
                                >
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                        <p>
                            We reserve the right to remove any content that
                            violates these terms or is otherwise objectionable.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Disclaimer -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:alert-triangle"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        Disclaimer
                    </h2>
                    <div class="space-y-4 text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        <p>
                            The materials on {SITE_TITLE} are provided on an 'as
                            is' basis. {SITE_TITLE} makes no warranties, expressed
                            or implied, and hereby disclaims and negates all other
                            warranties including, without limitation, implied warranties
                            or conditions of merchantability, fitness for a particular
                            purpose, or non-infringement of intellectual property
                            or other violation of rights.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            Further, {SITE_TITLE} does not warrant or make any representations
                            concerning the accuracy, likely results, or reliability
                            of the use of the materials on its website or otherwise
                            relating to such materials or on any sites linked to
                            this site.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <!-- Limitations -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:shield-off"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        Limitation of Liability
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        In no event shall {SITE_TITLE} or its suppliers be liable
                        for any damages (including, without limitation, damages for
                        loss of data or profit, or due to business interruption)
                        arising out of the use or inability to use the materials
                        on {SITE_TITLE}, even if {SITE_TITLE} or a
                        {SITE_TITLE} authorized representative has been notified
                        orally or in writing of the possibility of such damage.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Links -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:external-link"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        External Links
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        {SITE_TITLE} has not reviewed all of the sites linked to
                        its website and is not responsible for the contents of any
                        such linked site. The inclusion of any link does not imply
                        endorsement by {SITE_TITLE} of the site. Use of any such
                        linked website is at the user's own risk.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Modifications -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:refresh-cw"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        Modifications
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        {SITE_TITLE} may revise these terms of service for its website
                        at any time without notice. By using this website you are
                        agreeing to be bound by the then current version of these
                        terms of service. We encourage you to periodically review
                        this page for the latest information on our Terms of Service.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Governing Law -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-surface border border-border"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:landmark"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        Governing Law
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed">
                        These terms and conditions are governed by and construed
                        in accordance with applicable laws, and you irrevocably
                        submit to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts in
                        that location.
                    </p>
                </section>

                <!-- Contact Us -->
                <section
                    class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-br from-surface via-surface to-emerald-950/20 border border-emerald-500/20"
                >
                    <h2
                        class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-3"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon
                            icon="lucide:mail"
                            width="20"
                            class="text-emerald-400"></iconify-icon>
                        Contact Us
                    </h2>
                    <p class="text-neutral-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                        If you have any questions about these Terms of Service,
                        please contact us:
                    </p>
                    <a
                        href="mailto:blog.boopul@gmail.com"
                        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-emerald-500/10 border border-emerald-500/30 rounded-lg text-emerald-400 hover:bg-emerald-500/20 transition-colors"
                    >
                        <iconify-icon icon="lucide:mail" width="16"
                        ></iconify-icon>
                        <span>blog.boopul@gmail.com</span>
                    </a>
                </section>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Decorative Background Elements -->
    <div class="fixed inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div
            class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[600px] bg-gradient-to-br from-emerald-500/10 via-emerald-600/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute bottom-0 right-0 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-gradient-to-tl from-emerald-500/5 to-transparent rounded-full blur-3xl"
        >
        </div>
        <div
            class="absolute inset-0 bg-[linear-gradient(rgba(16,185,129,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(16,185,129,0.02)_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:64px_64px]"
        >
        </div>
    </div>
